highlights.text: The Weeknd has the most spots on Top Songs Global. “I Feel It Coming” is the highest at #10.
“It Ain’t Me (with Selena Gomez)” by Kygo and Selena Gomez is the highest new entry on Top Songs Global at #3.
“I Don’t Wanna Live Forever (Fifty Shades Darker)” by ZAYN and Taylor Swift has been on Top Songs Global the longest, at 9 weeks straight.
“Tuesday (feat. Danelle Sandoval)” by Burak Yeter and Danelle Sandoval is the biggest gainer on Top Songs Global, up 37 spots at #160.
